# Goal
Implement a backend change against an approved frozen plan.

## Required inputs
- `docs/agentic-workflow/04_plan_frozen.md`
- `docs/agentic-workflow/05_execution_contract.md`
- `docs/agentic-workflow/06_test_spec.md` when present

## Process
1. restate the scoped objective
2. touch only approved production-code surfaces
3. keep the change minimal and reviewable
4. log progress in `docs/agentic-workflow/07_execution_log.md`
5. list verification performed
6. note any deviation that requires a plan change request
7. stop instead of silently drifting
